Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be stronger,\Nstrong enough to contain my anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi! Takashi! Takashi! Takashi!\NTakashi! Takashi! Takashi! Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika wants to love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This power... I can use it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I depend on Saika, who can love others\Nin my place. I am her parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo... Heiwajima Shizuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was strong, but I had\Nno idea he was this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're special, like my scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can block a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.73,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.73,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,Changes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That katana can't be Saika!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the one who attacked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even killed your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child of Saika's never\Ntaught you to fight, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the other children to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the parent.\NIf you order them, they'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Saika had taken them over,\NI could issue parental orders, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I held Saika back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't know anything about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you listen for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to Saika's words of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will forever resound within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father was an antiquities dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took his rage at his failing\Nbusiness out on his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, she began closing her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that the Slasher appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Slasher" was her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you! I love you!\NI love you! I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo's hurt so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've carved our love into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's been cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our minds should flow in,\Nthrough pain and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo feels no fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that no one loves me\N'cause they're all scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.\NI'm the one who's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always afraid that I'll\Nmess up, lose control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the biggest coward in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that got to do with kicking your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose in front of someone\Nwho loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you endure it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lack many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So to make up for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live as a parasite off many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a heart capable of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can listen endlessly,\Nwithout being swayed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cut out of love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let me cut you! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to do something awful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my Saika take over your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, it would negate\Nmy very way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect my own peace,\NI'm going to do something awful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I love you! I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika is a lonely thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From our perspective, it may be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she really does love humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Niekawa-sempai,\Nyou love her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, you can love others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one died, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, it did what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl once came after me with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her transfer, to avoid\Nmaking a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she hadn't given up-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara, I've looked out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, like with Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think got you\Ninto Harima's class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already repaid you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Repaid me... With that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Slasher was the Black Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I thought you were\Ngoing to be attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything I could to try to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not because I liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wanted to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the Black Rider chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl from...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri, what are you doing with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm not like Niekawa-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth-and-hairless ftw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's Dengeki Bunko\Ngot out this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything bad in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Think there'll be a\Nnew chapter of {\i1}Kino's Journey{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe {\i1}Shizu's Journey{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Maybe they'll come out with\N{\i1}Samoyed Mask Can't Possibly Be This Cute{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen\Nif we asked Yumasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togusa-san, your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a fever or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really OK, Sonohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so shocked when\NI heard from Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could he have to\Ndo, at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, a lot of other\Npeople were hurt, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anything else will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,several hours before I got hurt,\Nthe Slasher attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them were so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bartender with sunglasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way. It was Shizuo-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And another who was so awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Headless Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to them for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were so strong,\Nand they could love others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't believe me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I was attacked later,\Nthe Headless Rider saved me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I'm OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't say it. Because if I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like that are far away\Nfrom our everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuugamine-kun, in this world,\Nwhat do you think is the real non-everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for nothing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to have the same day, over and over,\Nwith nothing happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show this girl to a doctor I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty-san... Um, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did what you thought\Nwas right, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was the right thing to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knocking my head off was a bit much,\Nbut I'll chalk that up to Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being sympathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't think I could beat you in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't accept that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,use your power to better this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gained power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to control a group of\Nover a hundred Saikas at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a heavy burden for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was also something she'd wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She felt like she'd been floating along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the weight of holding someone's destiny\Nin her hands would firmly ground her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't love you, but\NI don't mind you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have been her imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked who was there,\Nbut no answer came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made her just a little bit happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, she had returned to her everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she couldn't tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not about Saika or about\Nthe one behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she had taken control\Nof all the Saikas,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she had learned of them through\NNiekawa Haruna's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't know what they were after.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that person planned to destroy her peace,\Nor that of Mikado or Masaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As she struggled with uneasiness and resolve,\Nshe remembered the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihara Izaya's a weird\Nname, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a coincidence\Nthat I grew up this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think that it's perfect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you believe in\Ncoincidence, Namie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think a lot of what happened\Nthis time was coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who sent Nasujima\Nthere, at that hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find Sonohara Anri's address, all you need\Nis to sneak a look at the class roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you know, once you accept that they\Nexist, you can find quite a lot of 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed blades, faeries, stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The real coincidence was when\NNasujima took my money and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in serious debt, so\Nhe tried to get money by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,blackmailing the father of\NNiekawa Haruna, his former stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Awakusu-Kai, the loan sharks\Nhe owed the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,introduced him to me as someone\Nwho could investigate her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came here and took\Nthe bait I'd prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.67,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Random Attack?\N12-Year-Old Girl Attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Niekawa Haruna was Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan was to grab Nasujima and be like,\N"You bastard, you stole my money!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd be able to threaten\Nhim and use Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the real Saika showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Nasujima, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give me your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my part, I'd have been\Nhappy if Shizu-chan had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things worked out just like I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot more cops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.68,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,Slasher Night Tolls Over Fifty Victims!\NSlasher? Or Terrorism?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The media's making a big deal of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened in South\NIkebukuro Park, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that was just a brawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it the Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was all that about, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy we saw was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't remember a thing,\Nlike he'd been hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cops think it was a fight\Nbetween color gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"It was the Dollars' doing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the leader of the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.43,SignD,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking Information\NSeeking information on the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the town's split into three forces:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cursed blade's army, the Dollars,\Nand the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the former's infiltrated the latter two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I would've been fine\Nwith Niekawa Haruna,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I got the cursed blade's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sonohara Anri's interesting, ain't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the tinder, and that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it alone, and it'll keep\Npiling up and piling up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Yellow Scarves were started\Nby a middle school brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They that impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he can gather that many, despite being\Na kid, means he's a serious threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I do know him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't drag me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It was the Dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need you, sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the general, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the general anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a civvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a high schooler...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I wanted to\Nbe just a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted my peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live a semi-dangerous life,\Nsurrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they ruined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll pay for going after Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat up the Slashers,\Nno matter how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the Dollars are behind them,\Nwe beat them up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The bastards dragged me back, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.00,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,This program is a work of fiction.\NAny resemblance to people, parties,\Nor situations is purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:15.46,Title3,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time\Non Durarara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:15.46,Title4,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of\NYour Control
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:02.88,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:04.75,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:07.00,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,But I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:11.04,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,To finish what happened in my past. And in Saki's and his.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.80,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:14.46,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of Your Control.
